@page "/privacy"
@layout Layout.BlankLayout

<div class="min-h-screen bg-black text-white">
    @* Header *@
    <div class="border-b border-gray-800">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-8 py-6 flex items-center justify-between">
            <a href="/" class="text-lg font-bold tracking-wider">A<span class="text-blue-500">.</span></a>
            <a href="/" class="text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors flex items-center gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                     stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18" />
                </svg>
                Back to Home
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    @* Content *@
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-8 py-16">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-12">Last updated: March 15, 2026</p>

        <div class="space-y-10 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-300">

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">1. Introduction</h2>
                <p>Welcome to Abdulkareem Alabi's portfolio website. I respect your privacy and am committed to
                    protecting any personal data you share with me. This Privacy Policy explains what information I
                    collect, how I use it, and your rights regarding that information.</p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">2. Information I Collect</h2>
                    <p class="mb-3">I may collect the following types of information when you interact with this website:
                    </p>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 pl-2">
                        <li><span class="text-white font-medium">Contact form data:</span> Your name, email address, and
                            message content when you submit the contact form.</li>
                            <li><span class="text-white font-medium">Scheduling data:</span> Date and time preferences when you
                                book a call through the scheduling feature.</li>
                                <li><span class="text-white font-medium">Usage data:</span> Anonymous analytics such as page views,
                                    browser type, and device information collected automatically.</li>
                                    <li><span class="text-white font-medium">Cookies:</span> Small data files stored on your device for
                                        theme preferences and language selection.</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </section>

                                <section>
                                    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">3. How I Use Your Information</h2>
                                    <p class="mb-3">The information collected is used for the following purposes:</p>
                                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 pl-2">
                                        <li>To respond to your inquiries and messages submitted through the contact form.</li>
                                        <li>To schedule and confirm meetings or calls.</li>
                                        <li>To improve the website experience and understand how visitors interact with the site.</li>
                                        <li>To remember your preferences such as theme and language settings.</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </section>

                                <section>
                                    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">4. Data Storage & Security</h2>
                                    <p>Your personal information is stored securely and is only accessible to me. I implement appropriate
                                        technical measures to protect against unauthorized access, alteration, or destruction of your data.
                                        I do not sell, trade, or transfer your personal information to third parties.</p>
                                    </section>

                                    <section>
                                        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">5. Third-Party Services</h2>
                                        <p class="mb-3">This website may use the following third-party services:</p>
                                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 pl-2">
                                            <li><span class="text-white font-medium">Google Meet:</span> For scheduled video calls and meetings.
                                            </li>
                                            <li><span class="text-white font-medium">LinkedIn:</span> External links to my professional profile.
                                            </li>
                                            <li><span class="text-white font-medium">Email services:</span> For processing contact form
                                                submissions.</li>
                                            </ul>
                                            <p class="mt-3">Each third-party service has its own privacy policy governing the use of your
                                                information.</p>
                                            </section>

                                            <section>
                                                <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">6. Cookies</h2>
                                                <p>This website uses local storage and cookies to save your theme preference (light/dark mode) and
                                                    language selection. These are strictly functional and do not track your activity across other
                                                    websites.</p>
                                                </section>

                                                <section>
                                                    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">7. Your Rights</h2>
                                                    <p class="mb-3">You have the right to:</p>
                                                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 pl-2">
                                                        <li>Request access to the personal data I hold about you.</li>
                                                        <li>Request correction or deletion of your personal data.</li>
                                                        <li>Withdraw consent for data processing at any time.</li>
                                                        <li>Lodge a complaint with a data protection authority.</li>
                                                    </ul>
                                                </section>

                                                <section>
                                                    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">8. Contact</h2>
                                                    <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or wish to exercise your rights, please contact
                                                        me at:</p>
                                                        <p class="mt-3">
                                                            <a href="mailto:bdlkrmalabi@gmail.com"
                                                               class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 transition-colors">bdlkrmalabi&#64;gmail.com</a>
                                                        </p>
                                                    </section>

                                                    <section>
                                                        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
                                                        <p>I may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page with
                                                            an updated revision date. I encourage you to review this policy periodically.</p>
                                                        </section>

                                                    </div>
                                                </div>

                                                @* Footer *@
                                                <div class="border-t border-gray-800 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-8 py-6">
                                                    <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">&copy; ABDULKAREEM ALABI @DateTime.Now.Year. All rights reserved.</p>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>